title: Alex Jones Show - 2010 May 30 SU [sebaygo1]
description:

The Alex Jones Show
Sunday, 30 May 2010


[sebaygo1]



A live show today!

The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.


Wayne Madsen of the Wayne Madsen Report visits briefly mid hour 2, to discuss the likelihood that the recent torpedo attack on a South Korean naval vessel was a false flag operation.


Alex also takes a number of calls.
